body:
Make uninstall and install consistent.
@copiousfreetime 
\cc @drbrain

while reading [COC](https://github.com/rubygems/rubygems/blob/master/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md) I have noticed there:

> Instances of abusive, harassing, or otherwise unacceptable behavior may be reported by opening an issue or contacting one or more of the project maintainers.

it lacks the link to maintainers information, it would force anyone willing to report anything privately to search for the information and could discourage them from reporting.
